:0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T04:00:32.000Z","msg":"打籃球比條仆街跳起一野咬左落個頭殼頂<br />\n<br />\n依家頭頂重有個牙印係度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31ca3ea39ec55ddd0c204c2917105249e98494aa","tid":39733,"uid":10890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T05:32:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打籃球比條仆街跳起一野咬左落個頭殼頂<br />\n<br />\n依家頭頂重有個牙印係度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似和尚啲戒疤咁？"},{"pid":"d443d74a0f0fc5f672d6530acdee45f7fba7110d","tid":39733,"uid":23023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T07:13:19.000Z","msg":"小學個時同大我兩年既人隻揪<br />\n打到成手血 手背留左條疤係到<br />\n一留就留十年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3a807312615d330effd73a8f20f352896887e4b","tid":39733,"uid":22633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T10:58:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小學個時同大我兩年既人隻揪<br />\n打到成手血 手背留左條疤係到<br />\n一留就留十年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n想當年我仲讀緊BAND 3中學<br />\n<br />\n有條MK撚狗咁撚我, 話約我隻揪<br />\n佢以為自己有腹肌就好撚好打<br />\n(但其實我當時己經舉左兩三年鐵,一直有飲奶粉<br />\n不過我BULK緊, 即係夜神起義 Bane 果種大隻型<br />\n所以D肌肉線條未現到出黎)<br />\n我D 毒撚FD 嚇撚到標尿<br />\n「唔好同佢打呀, 佢有腹肌架」<br />\n「你痴左線咩, 你見唔見到佢幾咁FIT 呀」<br />\n我心諗話你怕你嬲<br />\n有腹肌唔等於有力量<br />\n我笑笑口咁答應左條MK 放學去籃球場打過<br />\nfast forward 去到決戰時間<br />\n成班同學企哂係側邊睇<br />\n佢就除左件校服<br />\n成個小丑咁係到谷佢果幾舊腹肌仔<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見到成班以為佢好好打果個情景,我真係快忍不住笑<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然最後佢打到我仆街, 牙都甩埋<br />\n但完全同腹肌冇關"},{"pid":"f01fd8453686249f5c0d8c74a5947e4821ccd051","tid":39733,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T11:04:53.000Z","msg":"bb 果陣比家姐拉左落床，跌穿個頭，縫左三針。<br />\n兩歲果陣支氣管炎入左院，腰後面有條四五cm 長既手術疤痕"},{"pid":"b603d47f735e9d49bdbc6c2e3665c5404308bdf6","tid":39733,"uid":21255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T11:06:15.000Z","msg":"細個俾街童聊<br />\n打交打到佢地拎cutter出黎<br />\n隻手俾佢劃左幾野"},{"pid":"3fdc7f58fb863222ade79a41a28ed06e08f96dfb","tid":39733,"uid":2950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T11:12:47.000Z","msg":"比蚊咬"},{"pid":"d12e8a83791b52ccad1e750110de948fa37438e4","tid":39733,"uid":30999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T13:31:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>斷右眉<br />\n細個係屋企跑冼到撞咗落枱角/牆角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我斷左眉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd2c2042ba21572ba336d8918649468556ab1b57","tid":39733,"uid":11255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T14:21:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>比蚊咬</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79fe87f0126c672c37434f94d78e0950a2c52e11","tid":39733,"uid":11255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T14:21:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>細個俾街童聊<br />\n打交打到佢地拎cutter出黎<br />\n隻手俾佢劃左幾野</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你就係廿八座大王？"},{"pid":"33736d1ff171b3f050bee7e7fe7aae4454734c9d","tid":39733,"uid":11255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T14:23:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>玩downhill炒左車<br />\n大肶&quot;la&quot;唔知比架單車咩位撞到<br />\n扯開左舊肉 個&quot;隆&quot;應該差唔多有手掌心咁大<br />\n如果過多一寸既話應該係個春袋穿&quot;隆&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後鏠左13針<br />\n個次真係好好彩  個醫生話個上傷口上少少就係大靜脈 咁都冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n勿相認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 聽到都春痛"},{"pid":"f2840927a8c6a534df094645afc82eb0d84e1334","tid":39733,"uid":11255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T15:44:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>打籃球比條仆街跳起一野咬左落個頭殼頂<br />\n<br />\n依家頭頂重有個牙印係度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似和尚啲戒疤咁？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢啲牙呢"},{"pid":"81c7b4d857d0c31f02fd0c16b32223cc6b92058f","tid":39733,"uid":32899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T15:50:55.000Z","msg":"大脾外則有幾tat<br />\n因為踢波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n岩岩琴日又整多tat<br />\n好撚痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50a6329c1fc9c51dbeca153b254e4debf1a57a5c","tid":39733,"uid":34352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T15:54:40.000Z","msg":"手指尾有點黑色<br />\n唔小心插到鉛筆<br />\n<br />\n&lsquo;失&lsquo;頭有個仆街既痕跡"},{"pid":"a5550ca8e316cc7c95bd583ed10ebf755ccece1f","tid":39733,"uid":29801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T23:04:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>玩downhill炒左車<br />\n大肶&quot;la&quot;唔知比架單車咩位撞到<br />\n扯開左舊肉 個&quot;隆&quot;應該差唔多有手掌心咁大<br />\n如果過多一寸既話應該係個春袋穿&quot;隆&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後鏠左13針<br />\n個次真係好好彩  個醫生話個上傷口上少少就係大靜脈 咁都冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n勿相認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 聽到都春痛</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實又冇咩野既<br />\n只係打唔到飛機 一打就牽動到個傷口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n忍左成個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09ed720cd2f32c04fac5ed4b9496200aa7bd29e2","tid":39733,"uid":27099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T03:30:30.000Z","msg":"想當年我仲讀緊BAND 3中學<br />\n<br />\n有條MK撚狗咁撚我, 話約我隻揪<br />\n佢以為自己有腹肌就好撚好打<br />\n<br />\n(但其實我當時己經舉左兩三年鐵,一直有飲奶粉<br />\n不過我BULK緊, 即係夜神起義 Bane 果種大隻型<br />\n所以D肌肉線條未現到出黎)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我D 毒撚FD 嚇撚到標尿<br />\n「唔好同佢打呀, 佢有腹肌架」<br />\n「你痴左線咩, 你見唔見到佢幾咁FIT 呀」<br />\n<br />\n我心諗話你怕你嬲<br />\n有腹肌唔等於有力量<br />\n我笑笑口咁答應左條MK 放學去籃球場打過<br />\n<br />\nfast forward 去到決戰時間<br />\n成班同學企哂係側邊睇<br />\n佢就除左件校服<br />\n成個小丑咁係到谷佢果幾舊腹肌仔<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n見到成班以為佢好好打果個情景,我真係快忍不住笑<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然最後佢打到我仆街, 牙都甩埋, 塊面仲有達&quot;la&quot;<br />\n但完全同腹肌冇關"},{"pid":"7fed5b49311d48e4e69d89d67627d612c4429f2b","tid":39733,"uid":6414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T03:38:41.000Z","msg":"背脊  大約10cm長<br />\n一出世氣管有事<br />\n本身屋企人以為哮喘<br />\n但睇極都搞唔掂<br />\n最後好似話係氣管同食道有個位有問題<br />\n要做手術先搞掂  唔係嘅話應該會係咁先<br />\n最後搞掂無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b9f29e7cb9c2db6ae3b325b1bcf7cab0529b359","tid":39733,"uid":65330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T04:08:24.000Z","msg":"右眼下面有一條打直既疤<br />\n<br />\n個陣有條友話我啤9佢，一拳打落我隻眼到<br />\n<br />\n因為我戴眼鏡副眼鏡比佢打碎左，<br />\n<br />\nD玻璃碎𠝹損左眼角同附近d位，最係係醫院聯左十幾針<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94770aa5de332738d1f31f87eceb69cfce73fdd3","tid":39733,"uid":11255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T04:09:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>玩downhill炒左車<br />\n大肶&quot;la&quot;唔知比架單車咩位撞到<br />\n扯開左舊肉 個&quot;隆&quot;應該差唔多有手掌心咁大<br />\n如果過多一寸既話應該係個春袋穿&quot;隆&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後鏠左13針<br />\n個次真係好好彩  個醫生話個上傷口上少少就係大靜脈 咁都冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n勿相認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 聽到都春痛</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實又冇咩野既<br />\n只係打唔到飛機 一打就牽動到個傷口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n忍左成個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n打飛機係上天賜比我地 冇得打好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2883d167b98d3458ab5b7b9adad1ba54e83ace6","tid":39733,"uid":48222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T04:26:15.000Z","msg":"電單車炒車<br />\n兩個膝頭，手掌，腰，腳趾，手踭加埋20幾撻疤<br />\n<br />\n戴眼鏡踢波，食波餅，左眉比眼鏡既鼻托𠝹開左，冇聯針，就咁用6塊膠布包住同埋搽獅子油，流左成個星期血<br />\n<br />\n細個比阿媽唔小心用較剪拮到左手食指對落"},{"pid":"d9e296b87016defe01a0cbd80a1deaf7286109fe","tid":39733,"uid":54387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T04:28:50.000Z","msg":"睇錯咗「作為一個痴漢」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64f4467db31771bcc725245f74a3d9bc7b90d066","tid":39733,"uid":30830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T04:32:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想當年我仲讀緊BAND 3中學<br />\n<br />\n有條MK撚狗咁撚我, 話約我隻揪<br />\n佢以為自己有腹肌就好撚好打<br />\n<br />\n(但其實我當時己經舉左兩三年鐵,一直有飲奶粉<br />\n不過我BULK緊, 即係夜神起義 Bane 果種大隻型<br />\n所以D肌肉線條未現到出黎)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我D 毒撚FD 嚇撚到標尿<br />\n「唔好同佢打呀, 佢有腹肌架」<br />\n「你痴左線咩, 你見唔見到佢幾咁FIT 呀」<br />\n<br />\n我心諗話你怕你嬲<br />\n有腹肌唔等於有力量<br />\n我笑笑口咁答應左條MK 放學去籃球場打過<br />\n<br />\nfast forward 去到決戰時間<br />\n成班同學企哂係側邊睇<br />\n佢就除左件校服<br />\n成個小丑咁係到谷佢果幾舊腹肌仔<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n見到成班以為佢好好打果個情景,我真係快忍不住笑<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然最後佢打到我仆街, 牙都甩埋, 塊面仲有達&quot;la&quot;<br />\n但完全同腹肌冇關</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21324e9a04414aa7b4dae599322e166ca987b89b","tid":39733,"uid":3271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T04:33:56.000Z","msg":"比電單車個引擎灼傷小腿內質 細個嗰陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8661554d8221a30c5ec8d79c353909d5bf9c4c8b","tid":39733,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T04:36:37.000Z","msg":"左手背一大撻<br />\n工傷夾爛手<br />\nd人嚇到仆街，我仲用右手拎手機同自己隻左手影相<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e16127013937e7e15bda433892af2f64232f180","tid":39733,"uid":8362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T04:45:25.000Z","msg":"細個坐人電單車尾，唔知點解成隻右腳捲入左個後輪，仲要絞左幾秒先拎到出來。成隻腳血肉模糊，仲見到條腳根<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 嚇到仆街。聽醫生講爭少少就會瘸。依家小腿至到腳底有個大疤痕。"},{"pid":"b4b55ec6997d4c468212719ac363d541de95d9db","tid":39733,"uid":4052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T06:23:15.000Z","msg":"小學果陣睇人打乒乓波，佢地打走左個波我沖出去幫佢地執波碌左落樓梯（4-5級），隻腳聯左5針。而家仲有條疤痕喺度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f004b63bb13c375648e568da0eab6f06d3f71f2f","tid":39733,"uid":44906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T06:26:33.000Z","msg":"岩岩出世就入左手術室係肚到開左刀<br />\n宜家一條長疤痕係個肚到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d20a1808c7bf976c2d26ad8bfa0fd3b9b1718e1","tid":39733,"uid":11255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T07:20:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>岩岩出世就入左手術室係肚到開左刀<br />\n宜家一條長疤痕係個肚到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c71e4e76b064e1ba3db34a1adb878393be181227","tid":39733,"uid":29801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T07:44:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 聽到都春痛</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實又冇咩野既<br />\n只係打唔到飛機 一打就牽動到個傷口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n忍左成個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n打飛機係上天賜比我地 冇得打好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我寧願傷多次都好過冇得打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f53131d86d5e301054561a025f651f18dae432a","tid":39733,"uid":62645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T07:46:03.000Z","msg":"割包皮..."},{"pid":"5411a4429bf24e314e39b12ebc28f7f5a9aa615d","tid":39733,"uid":32009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T07:59:19.000Z","msg":"細個去游水 淺水池咪有啲滑梯 我滑完諗住就咁爬返上去 跟住一仆 下巴爆左 成條滑梯都係血 之後仲封埋池<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好似10針"},{"pid":"f3c949b9b945dd1890c7ba095a1409f0bdebefcd","tid":39733,"uid":12070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T08:08:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n小學跳落床比支筆插親<br />\n仲有撻黑色嘢係腳</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n拎sick leave 冇帶筆可以用腳簽名</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好細，好似墨咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有冇變筆俠"},{"pid":"c97ab41f76f5e9a32209194b14d3117e5a28210a","tid":39733,"uid":37482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T08:20:49.000Z","msg":"第一次上廣州喺個有石仔嘅&quot;人造草&quot;球場打比賽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一野比人推低成個elbow磨薑咁磨 仲要是但搵啲運動tape包住就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n返到黎香港撕開嘅時候痛到屌哂老母咁<br />\n到依家嗰個位都仲有少少疤痕不過唔係好明顯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42d7f26344217a43271f437e7b96a5dc0ede47dc","tid":39733,"uid":30900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T08:25:47.000Z","msg":"上個禮拜<br />\n個陶瓷鉗啱啱拎嚟燒完嘢，唔記得咗佢仲好撚熱，一隻手包撚住咗隻鉗，當堂辣到右手手掌有條凹咗嘅深色疤<br />\n<br />\n不過我都好若無其事，淨係心底裡屌咗句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"597af59e23529afa0b73d536805cc25b9c7c9975","tid":39733,"uid":23619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T08:27:49.000Z","msg":"揸電單車炒車，頭落地，碌左幾圈，額頭，手，腳都有疤，次次飲少少酒啲疤都好紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d110fdf680ff3a17ac4093fb86f58d5217848129","tid":39733,"uid":55552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T08:36:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>揸電單車炒車，頭落地，碌左幾圈，額頭，手，腳都有疤，次次飲少少酒啲疤都好紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好有狂戰士feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55efea99e31d7246346b466982dfeed2182f362f","tid":39733,"uid":35104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T08:40:17.000Z","msg":"細細個係公園爬啲遊玩設施（到而家都唔知爬黎爬去個舊野叫咩名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />），跌左落黎跌斷左手<br />\n<br />\n前後做咗3次手術，手正中間位有條6cm長嘅疤<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5fb6ab0f9b168d96c549dd8f6fbe6f1b6d30687","tid":39733,"uid":55552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T08:52:49.000Z","msg":"個post睇到我好痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBTW我右手肘位有條兩寸長嘅刀疤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，係係我三歲嗰陣我老豆抱我玩單槓又走開接電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />搞到我唔夠力跌斷手入醫院開刀造成的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，不過就係靠住呢條猙獰嘅刀疤加上我溫柔之中帶著幾分殺氣嘅眼神，小學嗰陣成間學校無人夠膽蝦我，午膳啲女同學仲會嘴角含春咁偷偷地請我食甜品添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b79ab7714804b916d062a6c1182b9756b45d9516","tid":39733,"uid":46293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T10:05:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打籃球比條仆街跳起一野咬左落個頭殼頂<br />\n<br />\n依家頭頂重有個牙印係度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你係可立仔？？"},{"pid":"f80727f795da60e2465c873de1bc948a517a4972","tid":39733,"uid":25125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T10:22:06.000Z","msg":"細個坐嗰d俾小朋友玩既車仔(唔係bb車)<br />\n無啦啦前後倒轉坐<br />\n之後向後推<br />\n一下撞爆左張玻璃枱<br />\n玻璃打橫爆下巴<br />\n不過唔知點解又唔洗鏠針<br />\n條疤岩岩好係下巴最底<br />\n就咁正面睇根本睇唔到<br />\n算唔算不幸中之大幸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}